    <text>
        <body>
             <div type="edition" subtype="ogham" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="pgl-Ogam" resp="#POC"><!--update lang and resp here-->              
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1" style="text-direction:up-top-down"/><persName><name nymRef="#?">ᚋᚑᚇᚇᚐᚌᚅ<supplied reason="lost">ᚔ</supplied></name> <w type="formula" lemma="maqqas">ᚋᚐᚊᚔ</w> <name nymRef="#?">ᚌᚐᚈᚈᚐᚌᚅ<supplied reason="lost">ᚔ</supplied></name> <w type="formula" lemma="muccoviias">ᚋᚒᚉᚑᚔ</w> <name nymRef="#?">ᚂᚒᚌᚒᚅᚔ</name></persName>
                </ab> 
            </div>                    
            <div type="edition" subtype="transliteration" xml:lang="pgl-Ogam" xml:space="preserve" resp="#POC">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1" style="text-direction:up-top-down"/><persName><name nymRef="#?">MODDAGN<supplied reason="lost">I</supplied></name> <w type="formula" lemma="maqqas">MAQI</w> <name nymRef="#?">GATTAGN<supplied reason="lost">I</supplied></name> <w type="formula" lemma="muccoviias">MUCOI</w> <name nymRef="#?">LUGUNI</name></persName>
                </ab>
               <!-- <ab type="list"></ab>-->
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                <app n="1">   
                    <note>The inscription conforms to the 'X son of Y belonging to the family of Z' formula.</note>
                </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation">
                <p>'? son of ? belonging to the family of ?'</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                 <p>The inscription contains the formula words MAQI and MUCOI. MAQI is related to <ref target="https://dil.ie/31166">mac, macc</ref></distinct> 'son', and MUCOI is possibly related to <distinct xml:lang="sga"><ref target="https://dil.ie/31187">maccu, moccu</ref></distinct> 'belonging to the family of' (Stifter 2025). </p>
            </div>
